SELECT *
  FROM [dbo].AIA_IMS_BOB_WEEKLY_DATA_LOADS_CONSOLIDATION 
   WHERE AIA_IMS_BOB_WEEKLY_DATA_LOADS_CONSOLIDATION.Policy_ID NOT IN (SELECT 
      AIA_BOB_ALL_AGENCY_ALL_POLICY_ALL_TRANSACTION_ID_HISTORY.Policy_ID
